This is a "plugin" for the Video Disk Recorder (VDR).

Written by:                  Klaus Schmidinger <Klaus.Schmidinger@tvdr.de>

Project's homepage:          http://www.tvdr.de/remote.htm

Latest version available at: http://www.tvdr.de

